quran[18{c,v,t}:
44,1,h m
44,2,qasam hai iss kitaab Mubin ki
44,3,"ke hum ne isay aik barri kher o barket wali raat mein nazil kya hai, kyunkay hum logon ko mutnabba karne ka iradah rakhtay thay"
44,4,yeh woh raat thi jis mein har maamla ka hakeemana faisla
44,5,hamaray hukum se sadir kya jata hai hum aik rasool bhejnay walay thay
44,6,tairay rab ki rehmat ke tor par yaqeenan wohi sab kuch suneney aur jan-nay wala hai
44,7,asmano aur zameen ka rab aur har uss cheez ka rab jo aasman o zameen ke darmain hai agar tum log waqai yaqeen rakhnay walay ho
44,8,koi mabood uss ke siwa nahi hai wohi zindagi ataa karta hai aur wohi mout deta hai tumhara rab aur tumahray unn islaaf ka rab jo pehlay guzar chuke hain
44,9,( magar fi al waqea inn logon ko yaqeen nahi hai ) balkay yeh apne shak mein parre khail rahay hain
44,10,acha intzaar karo uss din ka jab aasman Sarih dhuwan liye hue aeye ga
44,11,"aur woh logon par chhaa jaye ga, yeh hai dard naak saza"
44,12,"( ab kehte hain ke )"" parvar-digaar, hum par se yeh azaab taall day, hum imaan laatay hain """
44,13,inn ki ghaflat kahan daur hoti hai? inn ka haal to yeh hai ke inn ke paas rasool Mubin aa gaya
44,14,"phir bhi yeh uss ki taraf multafit nah hue aur kaha ke"" yeh to sikhaya parhaya bawla hai """
44,15,"hum zara azaab htaye dete hain, tum log phir wohi kuch karo ge jo pehlay kar rahay thay"
44,16,jis roz hum barri zarb lagayen ge woh din hoga jab hum tum se intiqam len ge
44,17,hum inn se pehlay firaon ki qoum ko isi azmaish mein daal chuke hain unn ke paas aik nihayat shareef rasool aaya
44,18,"aur is ne kaha"" Allah ke bundon ko mere hawalay karo, mein tumahray liye aik amanat daar rasool hon"
